data.description: Large Pristine House with 6 foot privacy fence on Cul de sac in Beautiful Woodcreek North. Home Sits on 2 large lots at .61 acres to allow room to grow. Large bedrooms have 2 closets and the master has 3 for plenty of storage space. Roof and Interior Flooring has recently been replaced. Interior has fresh Paint. Gorgeous wrap around porch has fresh paint and pergola. Both are nice for sitting to watch the sun rise or set during coffee time. Fruit plants on the property include Grapes, Peaches, Pears,
